#: ../../guides/hooks-list.rst:504
msgid ""
"In ``elgg_view_page()``, filters ``$vars['head']`` Return value contains an "
"array with ``title``, ``metas`` and ``links`` keys, where ``metas`` is an "
"array of elements to be formatted as ``<meta>`` head tags, and ``links`` is "
