#: ../../guides/javascript.rst:751
msgid ""
"They prevent scripts from being loaded with ``defer`` or ``async`` "
"(performance)"
msgstr "Ils empêchent les scripts d’être chargés avec ``defer`` ou ``async`` (performance)"

#: ../../guides/javascript.rst:753
