#: ../../guides/menus.rst:57
msgid ""
"The third parameter passed into a menu handler contains all the menu items "
"that have been registered so far by Elgg core and other enabled plugins. In "
"the handler we can loop through the menu items and use the class methods to "
"interact with the properties of the menu item."
